      "updated": 1775302600324,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- User management (register /authenticate user , store profiles)\n- Virualbox CRUD (Create, read, update, delete cloud coding\nenvironments (React or Node types))\n- Sharing - share VirtualBox with other users by email , revoke access\n- Visibility control - Toggle VB between public and private\n- Realtime collaborative editing - Multiple users edit code simultanesuly\n- Integrated terminal\n- File Management \n- Generation Quota (Track and enforce a per-user limit of 30 AI code gnerations\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- User management (register /authenticate user , store profiles)\n- Virualbox CRUD (Create, read, update, delete cloud coding\nenvironments (React or Node types))\n- Sharing - share VirtualBox with other users by email , revoke access\n- Visibility control - Toggle VB between public and private\n- Realtime collaborative editing - Multiple users edit code simultanesuly\n- Integrated terminal\n- File Management \n- Generation Quota (Track and enforce a per-user limit of 30 AI code gnerations\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
