      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775302606574,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Low latency -  Edge-deployed serverless APIs\n- scalability - Handle many concurrent users/virtualboxes\n- security -  Authenticated access to dashboard and code editor\n- rate limiting - Prevent abuse of server resources\n- Reliability -  Graceful handling of inactive sessions\n- Data integrity -  Validated inputs at every API boundary\n- Real time consistency - Conflict-free",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Low latency -  Edge-deployed serverless APIs\n- scalability - Handle many concurrent users/virtualboxes\n- security -  Authenticated access to dashboard and code editor\n- rate limiting - Prevent abuse of server resources\n- Reliability -  Graceful handling of inactive sessions\n- Data integrity -  Validated inputs at every API boundary\n- Real time consistency - Conflict-free",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
